// comments

sysout + ctrl + SPACE ==> System.out.println();

data types:
type        size    primitive value        value
___        ____    _______________        _____
bool       1 bit    yes                    -128 to 127
int        4 bytes  yes                    -2 billion to 2 billion
double     8 bytes  yes                    fractional # up to 15 digits
char       2 bytes  yes                    single character/ASCII value 
string     varies   (no)reference          a sequence of characters
